{"tid":2122247,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青衣梁植偉紀念中學遭掟汽油彈    警追緝兩黑衣人","createTime":"2020-07-24T01:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T04:54:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9701254526ee820bdc937af2d4af002746664c","tid":2122247,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/G4H3UWg0c0Clvpo2Gtwjsg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/9f834840-cd45-11ea-b77f-0e8ea15eb347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FG4H3UWg0c0Clvpo2Gtwjsg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2F9f834840-cd45-11ea-b77f-0e8ea15eb347&h=ff67f5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(24日)凌晨零時58分，青衣長康邨樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學突然有火光冒出，並傳出爆炸響聲，上址近校門入口旁邊花槽位置，一時間火光熊熊，附近住客見狀紛紛報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報派出多輛消防車到場，並開喉將火救熄，初步毋須疏散亦無人傷，惟學校一個4米乘2米的花槽、一幅8米乘4米告示板，以及入口處幾幅玻璃屏風焚毀。消防在現場地上檢獲多個載有易燃液體的玻璃樽及鐵罐，相信遭人投擲汽油彈縱火，交警方接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，事發時，保安員目睹兩名穿黑色衫褲男子向校園投擲易燃物，得逞後向青衣西路逃去，葵青警區刑事調查隊正追緝兩名歹徒歸案，並調查犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n另據了解，今年5月間，該校有多塊玻璃屏風遭兩名少年砸毀，至於兩宗事件是否有關，有待警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r8Voc0VIxQPKzolRmAHtiA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/b9db83b0-cd45-11ea-b66f-12a10108b8c5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fr8Voc0VIxQPKzolRmAHtiA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2Fb9db83b0-cd45-11ea-b66f-12a10108b8c5&h=c144cf18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ee6UY5FDRYgTzXI8Yl6pLg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/ce57cec0-cd45-11ea-ab6d-70abf01aeb84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEe6UY5FDRYgTzXI8Yl6pLg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2Fce57cec0-cd45-11ea-ab6d-70abf01aeb84&h=2c192eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/青衣梁植偉紀念中學遭掟汽油彈-警追緝兩黑衣人-003620629.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%9D%92%E8%A1%A3%E6%A2%81%E6%A4%8D%E5%81%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%9F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AD%A6%E8%BF%BD%E7%B7%9D%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA-003620629.html&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6L%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=9851d0b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/青衣梁植偉紀念中學遭掟汽油彈-警追緝兩黑衣人-003620629.html</a>"},{"pid":"1313526ef4e02d8f812add85364702468c317695","tid":2122247,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"間學校關咩事"},{"pid":"7f99e771801f0aa135ab7f3b39608743e12414d8","tid":2122247,"uid":123774,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"校長二奶蘇州屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c4c5462c4f1255fec6090a67085a9a06db24d","tid":2122247,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"幫藍屍講埋：又係占中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011b7b567f5bc4ee155b8e4e2643de441d7c4f89","tid":2122247,"uid":100775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"咁突然既，得罪邊個？"},{"pid":"be45347f8edb8b45094f4ae00a53fe208a8c454d","tid":2122247,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"做咩搞間學校既，係咪校長叫雞無比錢？"},{"pi